        EWALD_TYPE spme
        ALPHA .44
        GMAX 25
        O_SPLINE 4
      &END EWALD
    &END POISSON_MM
  &END MM
  &SUBSYS
    &CELL
      ABC 24.955 24.955 24.955
      UNIT ANGSTROM
    &END CELL
